'''人蚤'''（'''''Pulex irritans'''''）是[[蚤屬|蚤屬]]下的一種[[跳蚤|跳蚤]]，雖然叫做人蚤，但實際也會寄生在其他動物身上。<ref>{{cite journal |title=A molecular phylogeny of fleas (Insecta: Siphonaptera): origins and host associations |author=Michael F. Whiting, Alison S. Whiting, Michael W. Hastriter & Katharina Dittmar |journal=[[Cladistics_(journal)|Cladistics]] |volume=24 |year=2008 |pages=1–31 |url=http://darwin.biology.utah.edu/china/PDFs/Fleas12.pdf |doi=10.1111/j.1096-0031.2008.00211.x |issue=5 |access-date=2014-08-18 |archive-date=2009-08-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090806205441/http://darwin.biology.utah.edu/china/PDFs/Fleas12.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>人蚤可能起源於[[南美|南美]]，原始宿主可能是[[豚鼠|豚鼠]]或[[西猯科|西猯科]]生物。<ref>{{cite journal |title=A biogeography of the human flea, ''Pulex irritans'' L. (Siphonaptera: Pulicidae) |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-biogeography_1989-03_16_2/page/115 |journal=[[Journal_of_Biogeography|Journal of Biogeography]] |year=1989 |volume=16 |pages=115–120 |jstor=2845085 |author=Paul C. Buckland & Jon P. Sadler |doi=10.2307/2845085 |issue=2}}</ref>除去人、狗、家貓等哺乳動物外，人蚤也會叮咬鳥類。它也是[[犬复孔绦虫|犬复孔绦虫]]的中間寄主。

